<h2>Welcome to VersionLab, <%= @user.name&.split(" ")&.first || "there" %>!</h2>

<p>
  Your free trial for <strong><%= @account.name %></strong> is now active.
  You have <strong>7 days</strong> and <strong>250 VL credits</strong> to explore everything VersionLab has to offer.
</p>

<h3>Getting Started</h3>

<ol>
  <li>
    <strong>Set your password</strong> &mdash;
    <%= link_to "Click here to set your password", @setup_url %> and log in.
    This link expires in <%= Devise.reset_password_within / 1.hour %> hours.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Create a template</strong> &mdash;
    Import an HTML email template or paste one in. VersionLab will parse it and identify the sections you can version.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Set up your audiences</strong> &mdash;
    Define the customer segments you want to target. The more detail you provide, the better the AI-generated versions will be.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Run your first merge</strong> &mdash;
    Select a template and audiences, then hit "Run." VersionLab's AI will generate tailored copy variants for each audience.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Review and export</strong> &mdash;
    Compare versions side-by-side, reject and regenerate any you don't like, then export the final HTML.
  </li>
</ol>

<p>
  If you have any questions, just reply to this email &mdash; we're happy to help.
</p>

<p>
  Best,<br>
  The VersionLab Team
</p>
